{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"WHATWG","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Glossary/WHATWG","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>WHATWG (<em>Web Hypertext Application Technology Working Group</em>) は<a href=\"https://spec.whatwg.org/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ウェブ標準の保守や開発</a>を行うためのコミュニティで、 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/DOM\">DOM</a>, Fetch, <a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/HTML\">HTML</a> などを扱っています。 Apple、Mozilla、Opera の従業員たちによって 2004 年に設立されました。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"learn_more","title":"詳細情報","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"general_knowledge","title":"一般知識","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Wikipedia の記事 <a title=\"WHATWG\" href=\"https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/Web_Hypertext_Application_Technology_Working_Group\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">WHATWG</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://whatwg.org/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">WHATWG ウェブサイト</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"詳細情報","id":"learn_more"}],"summary":"WHATWG (Web Hypertext Application Technology Working Group) はウェブ標準の保守や開発を行うためのコミュニティで、 DOM, Fetch, HTML などを扱っています。 Apple、Mozilla、Opera の従業員たちによって 2004 年に設立されました。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WHATWG","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"WHATWG","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"WHATWG","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"WHATWG","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"WHATWG","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"WHATWG","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"WHATWG","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/glossary/whatwg","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/glossary/whatwg/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","file